# DesInstalaci√≥n de Mongo en Linux - Ubuntu 14

## 1. Stop ElasticSearch
	
	p028036@POME:~$sudo service elasticsearch stop
	
## 2. Remove packages

	p028036@POME:~$sudo apt-get purge mongodb-enterprise*

## 3. Remove data directorios

	p028036@POME:~$sudo rm -r /var/log/elasticsearch

	p028036@POME:~$sudo rm -r /var/lib/elasticsearch
	
